    <text xml:id="Site_WFY_Section_Gb_Cave123">
        <body>
            <div type="cave" xml:lang="zh">
                <head>123號窟</head>
                <div>
                    <head>概述</head>
                    <div>
                        <head>位置</head>
                        <list>
                            <item>北岩，<foreign xml:lang="en">G</foreign>區（<ptr target="Fig_23_DSC_5193_stitch.jpg"/>）。</item>
                            <item>
                                <foreign xml:lang="en">F</foreign>壁方向：200°。</item>
                        </list>
                        <p>距臥佛東側約228米，位於當地居民吳純春家院後方的崖面之上。</p>
                        <figure rend="center" n="figure" xml:id="Fig_23_DSC_5193_stitch.jpg">
                            <head xml:lang="zh">隱沒在樹叢中的北崖<hi rend="bold">123</hi>號和<hi rend="bold">125</hi>號窟；2012年拍攝</head>
                            <head>Section of the northern cliff with caves <hi rend="bold">123</hi> and <hi rend="bold">125</hi> hidden among trees; photograph taken in 2012</head>
                            <graphic url="Fig_23_DSC_5193_stitch.jpg"/>
                        </figure>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <head>形制</head>
                        <list>
                            <item>敞口方形窟(<ptr target="Fig_25_DSC08349.jpg"/>)。</item>
                        </list>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <head>尺寸</head>
                        <list>
                            <item>窟口殘高117至183、寬222釐米，底部進深202釐米。</item>
                        </list>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <head>保存狀況</head>
                        <p>洞窟尚未完工，僅開鑿出下部及兩側，其內未寫刻文字。</p>
                        <ab>
                            <abbr>雷德侯</abbr>
                        </ab>
                        <figure rend="center" n="figure" xml:id="Fig_25_DSC08349.jpg">
                            <head xml:lang="zh">未完工的<hi rend="bold">123</hi>號窟；2010年拍攝</head>
                            <head>Half finished cave <hi rend="bold">123</hi>; photograph taken in 2010</head>
                            <graphic url="Fig_25_DSC08349.jpg"/>
                        </figure>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div type="cave" xml:lang="en">
                <head type="cave">Cave 123</head>
                <div>
                    <head>Description</head>
                    <div>
                        <head>Location</head>
                        <list>
                            <item>Northern slope, section G (fig. <ptr target="Fig_23_DSC_5193_stitch.jpg"/>).</item>
                            <item>Direction of wall f: 200˚.</item>
                        </list>
                        <p>Located 228 m to the east of the figure of the Reclining Buddha, in the cliff
                        behind and above the house of Wu Chunchun <foreign xml:lang="zh">吳純春</foreign>, a local resident.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <head>Shape</head>
                        <list>
                            <item>Box-shaped with open front (fig. <ptr target="Fig_25_DSC08349.jpg"/>).</item>
                        </list>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <head>Measurements</head>
                        <list>
                            <item>Remaining height 117-183 cm, width 222 cm, depth 202 cm.</item>
                        </list>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <head>State of preservation</head>
                        <p>Not finished, only the lower part and the two sides have been cut out
                        of the rock; no engraved characters.</p>
                        <ab>
                            <abbr>LL</abbr>
                        </ab>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
